    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fine, lightweight straw with a dull finish made from the young stalks of the species Corypha umbraculifera, from southeast Asia and the Philippines. Often used for hats.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
